    "body": "@jonasced This appears to be a different issue. Per this issue, starship will need to verify that rustup is in use before using rustup-specific version detection. Your issue concerns incorrect handling of overrides within the rustup-specific version detection. Please create a new issue.\r\n\r\nThese issues happen because starship includes rust version detection for rustup-managed toolchains that bypass the rustup-cli for better performance.",
